		<title>U.S. Dollar (USDX) is Still Under Pressure from Tariff Wars</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/en-za/analysis/market-news/us-dollar-is-still-under-pressure-from-tariff-wars</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 02:17:06 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Market news & Insights]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[DXY]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Recent news]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[XAUUSD]]></category>
